No, it was mostly left you know, to the - the older children, you know, me sister used to look after us a little bit, you know, when we were young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14766654 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16146915\charrsid12201700 Did you have any tasks you had to carry out regularly at home to help?

