Yes. Yes. Oh yes, I - we used to have - a greate here you know, one of those old fashioned leading grates you know what I mean, and I used to have that to do every Thursdays. Every Thursday, that was one of my jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14766654 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16146915\charrsid12201700 How old were you when you started?
