\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16146915\charrsid12201700  oil and - them sort of things but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14766654 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16146915\charrsid12201700 Did you have these sort of things regularly?
