Sunday. Well you'd got - you'd got - your Sunday clothes you know. Put them on on Sunday and then you'd start off the week with clean underwear, of course they used to wear pinafores in those days and - I - I k
now you got - you'd got to be very careful with your clothes, you know, you daren't go out and get dirty else you got a - clout. When you got in.
