ck of the police station, and - he used - me brother used to have to fetch this manure you know 'til he got - fed up with it. Well he found out that - it - he wasn't only getting manure for me father, he was getting it for the other gardeners as well. He 
was selling - he was selling it at so much a barrow the other men.
\par 
