\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6957354 R  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16146915\charrsid12201700 
Well I - I don't know, I think that - father was very strict, so was me mother, and you'd got to stand. I don't - perhaps we - perhaps we hadn't got enough chairs, I just can't remember - you know, to seat us all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14766654 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16146915\charrsid12201700 You couldn't bring toys or a book to the table?
