out of turn you know at school and - the teacher didn't half give me a clout and I - I said to the - turned round the teacher, I shall tell my mother when I got - when I get home. And when I got home and told me mother she gave me another one - for talkin
g in - for being cheeky and talking in class, so she was that type of a person you know. She wouldn't - you couldn't talk to her much. Her word was law.
