o
 keep her children, you know, used to cause a bit of strife that road about. He was a bit of a rot - well a piece of a rotter. I can remember that, he used to drink you know and - come home and knock me mother about. And - I can remember that and - and if
 we used to stick up for her you know he used to say, well you'll have to clear out. He just wanted his own - four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14766654 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16146915\charrsid12201700 So you couldn't have shared worries with him?
