 up and - and - I don't think he'd said anything about it to me own mother and - she didn't half give him a good hiding, you know. She - she wouldn't allow anything like that, you know, but I - I don't know whether he'd stolen them or what he'd done but -
 any rate this woman had been after these gloves.
